A game written in C as my university project. My implementation of game engine (gamma.c) involved 
implementation of structures
like stack (implemented as dynammic array) and find union (although not implemented explictly) and
algorithms like DFS.
Game can be played in two modes - interactive mode and by command line interface.
Writing command line (batch) mode of the game required writing a parser in C, and
implementing interactive mode of the game was an opportunity to learn about ANSI escape codes.
Project description can be found <link>
